<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>CodeSphere IoT</title>
    <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/a076d05399.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background: #0f172a;
            color: white;
        }

        /* Navbar */
        .navbar {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            background: #1e3a8a;
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            width: 100%;
            z-index: 1000;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }

        .navbar h1 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin: 0;
            color: #93c5fd;
        }

        .menu-icon {
            right: 40px;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            color: white;
            position: relative;
            padding: 10px;
            background: #3b82f6;
            border-radius: 31px;
            transition: background 0.3s ease-in-out;
            z-index: 1100;
        }

        .menu-icon:hover {
            background: #2563eb;
        }

        .dropdown {
            display: none;
            position: absolute;
            top: 94px;
            right: 73px;
            background: #172554;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            width: 200px;
            padding: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
        }

        .dropdown a {
            display: block;
            padding: 12px 16px;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #93c5fd;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: background 0.3s, color 0.3s;
        }

        .dropdown a:hover {
            background: #3b82f6;
            color: white;
        }

        .dropdown.active {
            display: block;
        }

        .container {
            display: flex;
            margin-top: 80px;
        }

        .sidebar {
            width: 250px;
            background: #172554;
            padding: 1rem;
            height: 100vh;
            overflow-y: auto;
            border-right: 2px solid #3b82f6;
            position: fixed;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        .sidebar h3 {
            color: #93c5fd;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .sidebar a {
            display: block;
            padding: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #93c5fd;
            font-weight: bold;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: 0.3s;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .sidebar a:hover {
            background: #3b82f6;
            color: white;
        }

        .content {
            flex-grow: 1;
            padding: 2rem;
            margin-left: 260px;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        h2 {
            color: #93c5fd;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .topic-section {
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }

        /* Responsive Styles */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .container {
                flex-direction: column;
            }
            .sidebar {
                width: 100%;
                height: auto;
                position: relative;
                border-right: none;
                text-align: center;
                display: none;
            }
            .content {
                margin-left: 0;
                width: 100%;
            }
            .sidebar.active {
                display: block;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- Navbar -->
    <div class="navbar">
        <h1>CodeSphere IoT</h1>
        <div class="menu-icon" onclick="toggleMenu()">â˜°</div>
        <div class="dropdown" id="dropdown-menu">
            <a href="/codesphere">Home</a>
            <a href="/profile">Profile</a>
            <a href="/ide">IDE</a>
            <a href="/block2">Progress</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Main Container -->
    <div class="container">
        <!-- Sidebar -->
        <div class="sidebar" id="sidebar">
            <h3>Topics</h3>
            <a href="#iot-basics">IoT Basics</a>
            <a href="#sensors-and-actuators">Sensors and Actuators</a>
            <a href="#iot-protocols">IoT Protocols</a>
            <a href="#iot-architecture">IoT Architecture</a>
            <a href="#iot-security">IoT Security</a>
            <a href="#iot-applications">IoT Applications</a>
            <a href="#iot-platforms">IoT Platforms</a>
            <a href="#iot-analytics">IoT Analytics</a>
        </div>

        <!-- Content -->
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Welcome to IoT Journey</h2>

            <!-- IoT Basics -->
            <div id="iot-basics" class="topic-section">
                <h3>IoT Basics</h3>
                <p>The Internet of Things (IoT) refers to the network of physical devices connected to the internet, collecting and sharing data.</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Sensors and Actuators -->
            <div id="sensors-and-actuators" class="topic-section">
                <h3>Sensors and Actuators</h3>
                <p>Sensors collect data from the environment, while actuators perform actions based on the data received.</p>
            </div>

            <!-- IoT Protocols -->
            <div id="iot-protocols" class="topic-section">
                <h3>IoT Protocols</h3>
                <p>IoT protocols like MQTT, CoAP, and HTTP enable communication between devices and the cloud.</p>
            </div>

            <!-- IoT Architecture -->
            <div id="iot-architecture" class="topic-section">
                <h3>IoT Architecture</h3>
                <p>IoT architecture consists of devices, gateways, cloud platforms, and applications working together.</p>
            </div>

            <!-- IoT Security -->
            <div id="iot-security" class="topic-section">
                <h3>IoT Security</h3>
                <p>IoT security ensures the protection of devices, networks, and data from cyber threats.</p>
            </div>

            <!-- IoT Applications -->
            <div id="iot-applications" class="topic-section">
                <h3>IoT Applications</h3>
                <p>IoT is used in smart homes, healthcare, agriculture, industrial automation, and more.</p>
            </div>

            <!-- IoT Platforms -->
            <div id="iot-platforms" class="topic-section">
                <h3>IoT Platforms</h3>
                <p>IoT platforms like AWS IoT, Google Cloud IoT, and Microsoft Azure IoT provide tools for managing IoT solutions.</p>
            </div>

            <!-- IoT Analytics -->
            <div id="iot-analytics" class="topic-section">
                <h3>IoT Analytics</h3>
                <p>IoT analytics involves processing and analyzing data generated by IoT devices to derive insights.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Script for Toggle Menu -->
    <script>
        function toggleMenu() {
            const dropdownMenu = document.getElementById("dropdown-menu");
            dropdownMenu.classList.toggle("active");
            const sidebar = document.getElementById("sidebar");
            sidebar.classList.toggle("active");
        }
    </script>

</body>
</html>